===Vector times vector===
The dot product formula_26 of two vectors formula_27 and formula_28 of equal length is equal to the single entry of the formula_29 matrix resulting from multiplying these vectors as a row and a column vector, thus: formula_30 (or formula_31 which results in the same formula_29 matrix).

